title: #TOURNOTES: PYZEL SHAPES
description: "Here's the theory: if you want to make a million dollars in shaping, start with $3 million. Then you're set!" More wisdom from Jon Pyzel (shaper to some of the North Shore's best, including John John Florence) in this edition of #TOURNOTES.
